examples.en: People raised a stink about the new law.
The whole factory stank of decaying fish.
Don't eat there  the food stinks!
She can sing, but her acting stinks.
He stinks of money and insincerity.
The toilets stank to high heaven (=stank very much).
Men who stink of beer really turn me off.
We had to work like stink to meet the deadline.
Activists have raised a stink about the shipments of nuclear waste.
